it.polimi.constraints.io.in.constraint

Class ConstraintReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.action.CHIAAction<O>
      • it.polimi.automata.io.in.XMLReader<Constraint>
        • it.polimi.constraints.io.in.constraint.ConstraintReader

  • public class ConstraintReader
extends XMLReader<Constraint>
    The ConstraintReader is used to load the constraint from an XML file. The XML files must be conform with respect to the XSD} file Constraint.xsd. The reader uses the ElementToPort, ElementToPortGraph and ElementToSubProperty transformers to convert the XML elements into the corresponding Java objects.
    Author:
    Claudio Menghi
